.com|accessdate=November 3, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180116055020/https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT205041|archivedate=January 16, 2018|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n|'''[[computer graphics|Graphics]]'''<br />''shared with main memory''\n|colspan=2|Nvidia [[GeForce 300 Series|GeForce]] [[Comparison of Nvidia graphics processing units#GeForce 300M (3xxM) series|320M]] using 256&nbsp;MB of DDR3 SDRAM\n|| Intel [[HD Graphics]] [[Comparison of Intel graphics processing units#Sixth generation|3000]] processor with 288&nbsp;MB of DDR3 SDRAM\n|| AMD [[Northern Islands (GPU family)|Radeon HD]] [[Comparison of ATI Graphics Processing Units#Radeon HD 6xxxM Series|6630M]] graphics processor with dedicated 256&nbsp;MB of GDDR5 memory\n|| Intel HD Graphics 3000 processor with 384&nbsp;MB of DDR3 SDRAM\n|colspan=3| Intel [[HD Graphics]] [[Comparison of Intel graphics processing units#Seventh generation|4000]]\n|| Intel HD Graphics 5000 processor\n|colspan=2| [[Intel Graphics Technology#Haswell|Intel Iris Graphics 5100]]\n|-\n|rowspan=2|'''[[Hard drive]]'''\n|| 320&nbsp;[[Gigabyte|GB]] 5400 rpm [[Hard disk drive|HDD]]<br /><span style=\"color:#969696\">''Optional 500&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD''</span>\n|| 2 \u00d7 500&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD\n|| 500&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD<br /><span style=\"color:#969696\">''Optional 750&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD''</span>\n|| 500&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD<br /><span style=\"color:#969696\">''Optional 750&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD, 256&nbsp;GB [[Solid-state drive|SSD]], or 1 \u00d7 256&nbsp;GB SSD + 1 \u00d7 750&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD''</span>\n|| 2 \u00d7 500&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD<span style=\"color:#969696\"><br />''Optional 2 \u00d7 750&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD, 1 or 2 \u00d7 256&nbsp;GB SSD(s), or 1 \u00d7 256&nbsp;GB SSD + 1 \u00d7 750&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD''</span>\n|| 500&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD<ref name=\"Mid 2012 MD387LL/A Apple Store\">{{cite web |title=Mac mini MD387LL/A (Late 2012) \u2013 Apple Store |date=October 23, 2012 |publisher=Apple I