93031/http://store.apple.com/us/configure/MD387LL/A |archivedate=October 25, 2012 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|| 1&nbsp;[[Terabyte|TB]] 5400 rpm HDD<br /><span style=\"color:#969696\">''Optional 1&nbsp;TB [[Fusion Drive]] or 256&nbsp;GB SSD''</span><ref name=\"Mid 2012 MD388LL/A Apple Store\">{{cite web |title=Mac mini MD388LL/A (Late 2012) \u2013 Apple Store |date=October 23, 2012 |publisher=Apple Inc. |url=http://store.apple.com/us/configure/MD388LL/A? |accessdate=October 23, 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025193041/http://store.apple.com/us/configure/MD388LL/A |archivedate=October 25, 2012 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|| 2 \u00d7 1&nbsp;TB 5400 rpm HDD<span style=\"color:#969696\"><br />''Optional 1 or 2 \u00d7 256&nbsp;GB SSD(s)''</span><ref name=\"Mid 2012 MD389LL/A Apple Store\">{{cite web |title=Mac mini MD389LL/A (Late 2012) \u2013 Apple Store |date=October 23, 2012 |publisher=Apple Inc. |url=http://store.apple.com/us/configure/MD389LL/A? |accessdate=October 23, 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025193053/http://store.apple.com/us/configure/MD389LL/A |archivedate=October 25, 2012 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|| 500&nbsp;GB 5400 rpm HDD<br /><span style=\"color:#969696\">''Optional 1&nbsp;TB [[Fusion Drive]]''</span>\n|| 1&nbsp;TB 5400 rpm HDD<br /><span style=\"color:#969696\">''Optional 1&nbsp;TB [[Fusion Drive]] or 256&nbsp;GB SSD''</span>\n|| 1&nbsp;TB [[Fusion Drive]]<br /><span style=\"color:#969696\">''Optional 2&nbsp;TB [[Fusion Drive]] or 256&nbsp;GB, 512&nbsp;GB or 1&nbsp;TB SSD''</span>\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\"| [[Serial ATA|SATA]] II (3 Gbit/s)\n| colspan=\"9\"| SATA III (6 Gbit/s)\n|-\n|'''[[Optical drive]]'''\n|| [[SuperDrive]] (writes: 6\u00d7 DVD\u00b1R-DL, 8\u00d7 DVD\u00b1R, 6\u00d7 DVD-RW, 8\u00d7 DVD+RW; reads: 8\u00d7 DVD\u00b1R, 24\u00d7 CD, 24\u00d7 CD-R and CD-RW\n|colspan=10| None included<br /><span style=\"color:#969696\">''(Optional External SuperDrive)''</span>\n|-\n|rowspan=5|'''Connectivity'''\n|-\n|colspan=11| 10/100/1000 Base-T Gigabit Ethernet\n|-\n|colspan=2| [[Bluetooth]] 2.1+EDR\n|colspan=9| [[Bluetooth 4]].0\n|-\n|colspan=2| Built-in [[IEEE 802.11n-2009|Wi-Fi 4]] (802.11a/b/g/n) 2\u00d72 chipset, up to 300 Mbit/s\n|colspan=6| Built-in [[IEEE 802.11n-2009|Wi-Fi 4]] (802.11a/b/g/n) 3\u00d73 chipset, up to 450 Mbit/s\n|colspan=3| Built-in [[IEEE 802.11ac|Wi-Fi 5]] (802.11a/b/g/n/ac) 3\u00d73 chipset, up to 1.3 Gbit/s\n|-\n|colspan=11|IR receiver\n|-\n|rowspan=7|'''Peripheral connections'''\n|-\n|colspan=5| 4x [[USB 2.0]] ports\n|colspan=6| 4x [[USB 3.0]] ports\n|-\n|colspan=2|[[Mini DisplayPort]]<br />''Supports one 2560\u00d71600 display''\n|colspan=6|[[Thunderbolt (interface)|Thunderbolt]] port<br />''Supports two 2560\u00d71600 displays''\n|colspan=6|2x [[Thunderbolt (interface)|Thunderbolt 2]] ports<br />''Supports two 2560\u00d71600 displays''\n|-\n|colspan=8|[[Firewire 800]] port\n|colspan=3|<span style=\"color:#969696\">''None''</span>\n|-\n|colspan=11|SDXC card slot\n|-\n|colspan=8| HDMI port<br />''Supports 1920x1200 output''\n|colspan=3| HDMI port<br />''Supports 3840\u00d72160/30&nbsp;Hz or 4096\u00d72160/24&nbsp;Hz output''\n|-\n|colspan=11| 3.5&nbsp;mm Line out/headphone jack, 3.5&nbsp;mm line-in jack\n|-\n| '''Latest release operating system'''\n| colspan=\"5\" | [[macOS High Sierra|macOS 10.13 High Sierra]]\n| colspan=\"6\" | [[macOS Catalina|macOS 10.15 Catalina]]\n|-\n|'''Noise'''<br />''at idle''\n|| 13 [[Decibel#Acoustics 2|dBA]] (2.4&nbsp;GHz)<br /><span style=\"color:#969696\">''15 dbA (2.66&nbsp;GHz)''</span>\n|| 15 dBA\n|colspan=2| 16 dBA\n|| 17 dBA\n|| 12 dBA<ref name=\"macmini2012spec\">{{cite web|url=https://www.apple.com/mac-mini/specs.html|title=Apple - Mac mini - Technical Specifications|date=January 4, 2013|accessdate=November 3, 2017|url-status=bot: unknown|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130104110531/http://www.apple.com/mac-mini/specs.html|archivedate=January 4, 2013|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|| 15 dBA<ref